Just above the body is one location where we can add

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:08.435
JavaScript and is also

00:04:08.435 --> 00:04:11.050
over locations which we'll look at soon.

00:04:11.050 --> 00:04:14.340
Earlier when we were inside the console,

00:04:14.340 --> 00:04:16.745
remember we looked at selecting

00:04:16.745 --> 00:04:20.170
each particular element with dollar symbol zero.

00:04:20.170 --> 00:04:23.710
Also remember we said that this is unique to the console.

00:04:23.710 --> 00:04:25.610
We need a different way of selecting

00:04:25.610 --> 00:04:28.625
our elements inside of the text editor.

